formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. Reliance has been laid on the Partner's representation for carpet area of the units sold/unsold as required in the Annexure to the certificate. 
2. Reliance has been laid on the Partner's representation for estimated cost of the project. 
3. The figures and values are based on unaudited books presented before us till 30.11.2022. Members and RERA AC details are till 30.11.2022. 
4. Work done as per engineer's certificate is not reflected in form 3 via auto population.
5. As the Agreement to sale were not available for physical verification, reliance has been placed on Management representation. 
6. Excess amount has been deposited in RERA account. The same has been considered for withdrawal. 
7. Partner's representation is relied for bifurcation of site expenses viz-a-via office expenses so consideration of Site expenses. 
8. The stamp duty expenses has not been provided in books and borne but paid by purchaser and hence no effect has been given to that extent.
9. There is difference in area in sale deed of land and plan passing by 9sq mtrs. For the purposes of the certificates and agreement actual rea of land as per sale deed is considered.
10. The project is completed and BU is received.
